9. Using where condition with multiple operations:
```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    condition = np.greater(bins, item)
    part1 = np.where(condition, np.exp(bins), np.zeros_like(bins))
    part2 = np.log(1 + np.sin(np.pi * item / (bins + 1)))
    return part1 + part2
```

